body:
Ok so, I was bronze 5 last season and i understood why. Flamin teammates and what not. I took a few months off and decided to come back a couple of months ago. So I began to play again after watching couless streams and analysing them. I went from Bronze 5 this season to bronze 3 in about 2 days. Then I had a win but lost 3 games so i got dropped back to B4. 

I have 31 wins and 21 losses so far but for so ungodly known reason i am only earning 17 LP but losing 21???? I dont get it. if the system registered that &quot;Oh he is actually doing quite well maybe he should be advancing&quot; but no its more like &quot;LOL F*CK YOU&quot;

Can someone kindly explain why this is happening, thank you :)
